The overall website will be teaching you about different types of storms such as Tornados, Hurricanes, Tsnuami etc. 
At the top of the website there will be a navigation bar where you can choose which storm to learn about
Below this you will have fun facts about tsunamis telling you about the speed of them, how they're caused, and how they are measured or detected.
All around the facts will have pictures of tsnuamis and other storms
At the footer of the webpage there will be any other information about storms and contact information.
